571
00:23:51,821 --> 00:23:53,432
Yes. Yes.

572
00:23:53,475 --> 00:23:56,826
- Yay!
- Oh, my God! Wow!

573
00:23:56,870 --> 00:23:58,915
Whee!

574
00:23:58,959 --> 00:24:02,658
Yes, yes, yes.

