581
00:24:37,301 --> 00:24:41,697
♪ Oh, oh, oh,
our love carries on ♪

582
00:24:41,741 --> 00:24:45,658
♪ So go, go, go
back where you belong ♪

583
00:24:49,923 --> 00:24:53,492
♪ When you're looking up
